author: @saiash2908
text:
been back here after few months and it just made me remember those times in my personal life during september 2023 when this song first released at that time i hadnt listened to much of hassan's earlier discography and this song was one of my least anticipated ones from the ep as it had huge features on it which attracted me at first. but this song impacted me it is attached to that phase of my life when i was just in a systematic race and just moving forward facing all the emotional changes in my personality this one helped me go through them and thats what matters for me the most this might not be the most technically perfect song my ears ever listened to it had few lines that initially i didnt even understood but still it hooked me up and i guess thats what is the role of music to hook peoples memories in those rescords in which artists had pour their hearts and souls and honestly thats why i can say that this one song made me realise what music does to a person and why is good music important
thanks to hassan and talwinder
